<!--
  A simple behavior tree that replans at 1Hz. Recovery consists of waiting (drifting while hovering)
  for a few seconds. Orca4 doesn't use costmaps, so there's no need to clear them.
  RateController re-calculates the path iff the lookahead-distance CANNOT reach the deired path.
  Starting point: navigate_w_replanning_and_recovery.xml
-->

